To explain how CEDEX will establish a two-sided market for diamond trading, Section 4.1 specifies the mechanism 

for uploading diamonds to the platform for subsequent trading. Section 4.2 focuses on buying and selling individual 

diamonds. Finally, Section 4.3 describes the way CEDEX users may take possession of physical diamonds.

