APPENDIX C - EXECUTION & BUSINESS ROAD MAP 

The CEDEX project was launched at the beginning of 2017. The CEDEX team has already achieved extensive 

business and technological milestones, as illustrated in Fig. 10.

In October 2017, TechFinancials announced the project to the public. AIM Announcement October 23, 2018

Below we have detailed the four milestones that are the building blocks of the CEDEX project. 

Q4 2017 MILESTONE 1 – THE DEX 

The first milestone and major achievement of the CEDEX technology and diamond teams is the creation of an alpha 

version of the DEX. As explained in detail above, the DEX is an algorithm that compiles all relevant market and 

technical data and creates a machine-learning engine to evaluate a diamond’s market price and rate its asking price 

accordingly. The alpha version of the DEX is already operational on the cedex.com website.

Q4 2018 MILESTONE 2 MVP LAUNCH (MINIMAL VIABLE PRODUCT) OF THE CEDEX PLATFORM

The second milestone is to finish the MVP product, complete the regulatory framework for launching the product in 

the first locale and start marketing activities in order to drive traffic to the platform. The MVP will allow traders to buy, 

sell or take physical delivery of a diamond. 

